data.description: *ATTENTION INVESTORS* Charming cottage located in a quiet neighborhood in the Charpentier district also referred to as the Garden District. This home is within walking distance of all downtown has to offer. Enjoy local restaurants, downtown events, and the lake front. It is well maintained with original wood floors and displays its historic character. The open-concept living area provides a welcoming atmosphere for relaxation and entertaining. This 3 bed, 2 bath home with a little lipstick and rouge would make a great investment property. The downtown area is continuing to expand and now would be a great time to become a part of it. The only thing that you need to do is sit back relax and enjoy your new home! This home is located in flood zone "X", where typically flood insurance is not required. All measurements are M/L. Give me a call today to set up a showing and "Say Yes To The Address".
